<div class="col-lg-6">
    <div class="description wow">
        <h2 class="orange-text h2-responsive wow fadeInLeft">Welcome to Autism Talks</h2>
        <hr class="hr-dark">
        <p class="wow fadeInLeft red-text" data-wow-delay="0.4s" style='font-size: 17px;'>Autism Talks is a website for allies of those with autism and who 
          wish to find and share useful information they have found about autism.
          This is a site made to help inform the families and friends so they
          may inform themselves to help the people they love that are autistic.
          I hope you make find the information shared useful and enjoy your time!</p>
        <br>
        <a href='#best-features' class="btn btn-primary wow fadeInLeft learn-button" data-wow-delay="0.7s">Learn more</a>
    </div>
</div>
<div class="col-lg-6 categ-card">
  <div class='card'>
    <% if !@category.nil? && @category.name != 'Category'%>

      <% if @category.articles.empty? %>
        <p class='amber-text'>There are no articles posted under this category. Maybe you want to post one?</p>
      <% else %>

        <ul>
          <% @category.articles.each do |article| %>
            <li class='article-link'><a href='<%= article.link %>' class='amber-text'><%= article.title %></a></li>
          <%end %>
        </ul>

      <%end%>
      
    <% end %>
  </div>
</div>
